== Data Structure ==

=== Combination Table Format ===

ROM address: $01c200, size: 512 bytes ($200)

Each combination entry uses 2 bytes:
{| class="wikitable"
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Item ID for combination lookup (ItemA + ItemB index)
|-
| $01 || 1 || Result Item ID
|}

The table is indexed by: <code>(Item1_ID * 16) + Item2_ID</code> mod 256

=== Invention Recipe Format ===

Each invention recipe uses 8 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Result Item ID
|-
| $01 || 1 || Material 1 ID
|-
| $02 || 1 || Material 1 Quantity
|-
| $03 || 1 || Material 2 ID
|-
| $04 || 1 || Material 2 Quantity
|-
| $05 || 1 || Material 3 ID
|-
| $06 || 1 || Material 3 Quantity
|-
| $07 || 1 || Required Level / Flags
|}

